description: A witness says one of the planes burst into flames after coming down not far from the city of Tours.
title: France plane crash: Five killed after mid-air collision near Tours
title_page: France plane crash: Five killed after mid-air collision near Tours - BBC News
maintext: Witness Genevieve Allouard-Liebert, who lives in the area, said she had heard a "big crash" when the planes came down. She said she and her husband saw a man fall from the larger plane as it skimmed nearby rooftops.
